text: José Francesch (18 August 1908 - 22 August 1964) was a Spanish swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1964 deaths Category:Spanish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Spain Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers from Barcelona Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
